snippet.title: Council of Geeks
snippet.description:
On this channel we examine various aspects and impacts of geek fandom/culture through some genderfluid person ranting at the camera, the occasional group discussion, and if you go WAY back there's even some scripted shorts.

If it's geeky, they'll probably talk about it. 

Remember, YOU are the council, they only run the meetings.
